HEADLINE: From Hours of Manual Work to Instant Insights

THE PROBLEM (BEFORE):
Every customer repair generates data — but reading it meant
downloading Excel files, building charts manually, and spending
hours just to answer: "What's going wrong, and where?"

THE SOLUTION (NOW):
A live, browser-based dashboard that answers that question
in seconds — automatically, every single day.

WHAT IT COVERS:
→ Defect rate tracked day-by-day and week-by-week
→ Top symptoms, repair parts, locations, and service centers
→ Domestic vs. Export market breakdown — side by side
→ Built for any model launch, not just one phone


